import { View, Text } from 'react-native'
import React from 'react'

export default function HireNow() {
  return (
    <View style={styles.container}>
    <View style={styles.hireTopCotainer}>
       <ImageBackground source={HeaderBgImage} resizeMode="cover" style={{flex:1}}>
           <View style={styles.titleContainer}>
               <Text style={styles.hireTitle}>THE LARGEST</Text>
               <Text style={styles.hireTitle}>EQUIPMENT RENTAL NETWORK</Text>
           </View>
       </ImageBackground>
    </View>
    <View style={styles.hireBottomCotainer}>
           <View>
              <Image style={styles.loginIcon} source={loginIcon} />
           </View>
           <View>
             <Text style={styles.hireCodeTitle}>VERIFY YOUR OTP</Text>
           </View>
           <View>
              <TextInput style={styles.otpInput}/>
           </View>
           <View style={{flex:0.2,flexDirection:"row"}}>
             <Text style={styles.hireCodeTitle}>disn't get OTP yet, </Text>
             <Text  style={styles.hireCodecolor}>RESEND OTP</Text>
           </View>
           <View>
              <Button onPress={()=> handleSubmit()} style={styles.cusLogin} label="LOGIN" bgColor="#f6921e" color="#fff" onPress={handleSubmit} />
           </View>
    </View>
</View>
  )
}
